How do I check which profile I have actively running?

	tuned-adm active
	
How do I check available profiles?

	tuned-adm list
	
How do I get more info about a profile?
	
	tuned-adm profile_info profile_name
	
How do I switch profiles for my system?
	
	tuned-adm profile PROFILE_NAME

If you're indecisive, you can ask the system for its opinion on which profile to use

	tuned-adm recommend
	
Of course, you can turn off tuning

	tuned-adm off
